"<https://github.com/tarantool/tarantool/issues/2301>`_."

msgid ""
"tarantoolctl: ``start``, ``stop`` and ``restart`` commands now redirect to "
"``systemctl start/stop/restart`` when systemd is enabled. Issue `2254 "
